            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1695849118500-c8034bc651b6?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1887&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="nature image">
